	(text "$A000-$BFFF: asserts RAS, XPM=1, CS=0, ROM signaling (\"ROM\" slot or Direct)\n$1000-$3FFF: asserts CAS, XPM=0, CS=0, RAM signalling (\"RAM-1\" slot or Direct)\n$1000-$3FFF: asserts CAS, XPM=0, CS=1, RAM signalling (\"RAM-2\" slot)\n$C000-$DFFF: asserts RAS, XPM=1, CS=1, ROM signalling (\"DISK\" slot)\nCarts are active when ~{CS} is low.\nExpansion module: ~{XPM} selects RAM slots when low, ROM slots when high.\nExpansion module: uses ~{CS} to select front/back slot pair,\nenabling only one slot's ~{CS}.\nHW Registers in ROM space: \\CAS is the Write strobe."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
